channel.title: Sparc Mac, Win All Day, Fred... etc. on RuneScape
channel.description:
Okay so I was cooking as I'm trying to get 99 cooking since it would suit my name, and someone says "Omg Taco Limey is in his chat" so I go in it and there he is ;P.. I got a video and a shitload of screenshots of him and other people's usernames that I found rare. Can't find that old 'rare username' topic and don't want to bump it.
He's still live broadcasting, google 'taco limey live broadcast' it will be there, he's on world 54 dicing and staking and sparc mac is there, not sure if he's still there though.
Pics *removed you people dont need to know my username*

item.dc:creator: @the_elve_age the elve age
item.description:
@the_elve_age wrote:

[quote=“Fridder, post:23, topic:407771”][quote author=IlikeArrays link=topic=509048.msg3695173#msg3695173 date=1312391843]

Ehh Ill show you real legends… who wants to meet s a x and ladykilljoy? I have a direct line to them if anyone is interested.

I don’t know who either of those people are, unless ladykilljoy is the really rich one.

Ladykilljoy before she quit stacked up on rares and I mean stacked… she showed me a full inventory of purple party hats one day only to leave my mind guessing for the rest. S a x and ladykilljoy played rs from 2001-2003 in their prime and dominated the rsc wildy highscores. s a x still actively plays the game and ladykilljoy quit in I believe 2005-2006. She logs in every now and then and usually a group of friends get to see her. If anyone cares… she works as a web designer for multiple car companies, including Porsche, Honda, and Ford.

[/quote]

Do you know why she quit by any chance?[/quote]
Most people from 01-03 quit of boredom, or they’ve grown out of it.
